stuffs.name: Train car above the bridge
stuffs.description: I hid army supplies in a train car during regrouping. Not to forget.

stuffs.name: Things belonging to the one who perished in the anomaly
stuffs.description: I saw a stalker go down under an anomaly by the train tunnel in the woods. Seemed like he had some pretty good stuff.

stuffs.name: The cross by the bandits' camp
stuffs.description: I hid the habar by the bandits' camp under the cross

stuffs.name: Bandits' warehouse
stuffs.description: The chest stolen by the bandits has been found in the cellar of the central building. Need to prepare a detachment and get it.

stuffs.name: Under the cross
stuffs.description: When my comrades and I were fighting off the dogs in uniform, I buried some goods under the bridge. Let them stay there for now.

stuffs.name: Shelter in the cellar
stuffs.description: I stuck the backpack in the cellar. I'll be back later - can't get to it right now.

stuffs.name: Safe on the farm
stuffs.description: I found a half-buried safe on the farm. I'll keep the goods there for now.

stuffs.name: Container in the train car
stuffs.description: A little bird told me that somebody's hiding something in the train car on the bridge. Will need to check it out on the way back. I wonder who...

stuffs.name: Goods of the shooter
stuffs.description: Hid the goods right under the roof of the little house by the bridge.

stuffs.name: Things by the bridge
stuffs.description: Hid my crap in one of the chests not far from the bridge. That's it, I'm calling it quits and leaving the Zone. Farewell, brothers! I'll never forget the motherland.

stuffs.name: The backpack is near the village
stuffs.description: One of the stalkers choked by the newbies' camp. Check out his goods.

stuffs.name: Cellar in the village
stuffs.description: Found out from Lihoi that the secret stash is in the cellar. He was talking too much so we shut him up for good.

stuffs.name: A good place
stuffs.description: Found a great hiding place in the cellar. I'll wait until someone puts something there.

stuffs.name: Vorpal's secret stash
stuffs.description: Found out from Vorpal that there's a secret stash in the cellar. Our men were carrying out a scouting expedition in the area. Let's check it out.

stuffs.name: The valuables of the commander
stuffs.description: They saw that the commander has a tricky chest in his office, and there's a ton of valuable goods there.

stuffs.name: By a country road
stuffs.description: Some stalker croaked not far from the camp of the newbies. We should see what he was carrying. Who lets them in here anyway?

stuffs.name: The robbers' cellar
stuffs.description: The goodies are hidden in the bandits' cellar. They weren't there before so let's wait for the right time to take them all.

stuffs.name: Gas pipe
stuffs.description: Discovered the inventory in the pipe, not far from the farm. Once the stockade is over, I'll definitely come back.

stuffs.name: Hidden things
stuffs.description: Threw my backpack off not far from the post, should pick it up as soon as possible, before the commander transfers us to a new location.

stuffs.name: Tower at the check-point
stuffs.description: I left the chest at the tower for now. Will pick it up when I can.

stuffs.name: Bandits' storage
stuffs.description: I saw how a bandit hid his goods in a chest in the hangar. How can I quietly steal it?

stuffs.name: Old crane
stuffs.description: Vasya and I went to check things out and suddenly a bullet hit him. And I had nothing to do with it. It's the damn bullet. I hid the stuff away in a pipe.

stuffs.name: Grizzly's things
stuffs.description: Grizzly croaked with all of his stuff at the Garbage, in the train tunnel behind the diesel. Pity about Grizzly.

stuffs.name: Pipe on the North pile
stuffs.description: Stowed the goodies away in a pipe at the garbage.

stuffs.name: Extra cash in the scrap metal
stuffs.description: The things are in the garbage, in one of the pipes. If you don't know exactly where they are, you won't find them.

stuffs.name: Iron furnace next to the cistern.
stuffs.description: I hid the stuff in a metal pipe next to the two cisterns. I should pick it up, but don't have the time.

stuffs.name: Pipe on the East pile
stuffs.description: There are some useful things hidden among the radioactive waste, where few hang around.

stuffs.name: Nobody's backpack
stuffs.description: Someone's backpack is lying around in the valley, with anomalies all around. How could you get to it?

stuffs.name: The belongings of the murdered one
stuffs.description: Finished off the traitor in the swamp... we buried him there too and left his goodies under the cross. Had more important things to worry about.

stuffs.name: Rotted stump
stuffs.description: There's a secret stash in the shadows - a good place to hide it.

stuffs.name: Log in the forest
stuffs.description: There's a log in the forest with a hold inside. In the hole there's treasure - it's time to get it.

stuffs.name: Storage of the Strelok faction
stuffs.description: Petrenko wanted to pass on the word that there's information about the secret stash of the Strelok faction at the Garbage. Here in the valley floor there has to be a manhole, he explained how there's a trick to opening it. As soon as everything calms down, we gotta go there check it out.

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the car
stuffs.description: Hid it in the car, the Long One said it was a good place.

stuffs.name: Stalker's backpack in the bus
stuffs.description: Put the backpack in the bus - seems unnoticeable

stuffs.name: Assorted supplies
stuffs.description: I put the supplies in the chest, and the chest into the old house around the corner. Still can't understand what that structure is for.

stuffs.name: Safe in the South pile.
stuffs.description: There is a safe partially buried in a pile of trash. Everything's in the safe. Better not forget what was in it.

stuffs.name: Storage in the scrap metal yard.
stuffs.description: Put the goodies on the pile of trash in the pipe

stuffs.name: Supplies in the chest
stuffs.description: The head of radio communications passed along a message to us: retreat. I found a chest, threw in what I had on me, and retreated empty-handed.

stuffs.name: Pipe by the bus
stuffs.description: I stuck the habar into the pipe at the garbage. It won't stay there for long.

stuffs.name: Backpack in the ruins
stuffs.description: It's easy to hide the backpack in the ruins. I hope it won't be hard to pick it up, if the bandits don't get in the way.

stuffs.name: Chest at the heavily armed military checkpoint
stuffs.description: While the dutyers were shooting, I hid the habar in the train car. Somehow I have to get in to pick it up. And to thank the Duty.

stuffs.name: Backpack of Weakling
stuffs.description: They say that Weakling choked at the Garbage - need to drop by to check out the goods. Otherwise there'll be many interested parties coming in.

stuffs.name: String bag in the pothole
stuffs.description: For now I'll hide the goods in the pothole. Maybe they won't find them.

stuffs.name: Under the dipper
stuffs.description: An anomaly got someone by the escalator - the backpack is in view, but hard to get to.

stuffs.name: The extra cash is under the concrete blocks
stuffs.description: Barely made it under the beams, but at least the backpack's well hidden - nobody will try to climb in here.

stuffs.name: Seriy's secret stash
stuffs.description: For now our secret stash is in the tunnel. That's a good place - few know about it, and the anomalies will keep others from getting in.

stuffs.name: Stump with hole
stuffs.description: I hid it in the stump by the tunnel. There's a good hole there.

stuffs.name: The mark is under the cross
stuffs.description: I buried some goodies under the cross by the bush.

stuffs.name: Backpack under tree
stuffs.description: Dropped the backpack under the fallen tree.

stuffs.name: Backpack of a chimney sweeper
stuffs.description: Stuck the backpack into the pipe by the factory. Nobody will find it.

stuffs.name: Chest on the roof
stuffs.description: Stashed the chest on the roof of the factory - that way nobody will find it. Problem is, it will rust under the rain.

stuffs.name: Drunkard's backpack
stuffs.description: They were shooting. Had to drop the backpack under the train car behind the seat. At least I got away. I'll go back and get it.

stuffs.name: By the three cisterns
stuffs.description: Hid it under the cross, behind the cisterns. Dig a little, just don't get carried away.

stuffs.name: Backpack is in the porthole
stuffs.description: I put the backpack towards the top at the factory, that way nobody will see it. Problem is, I don't exactly remember what's in it.

stuffs.name: Radioactive chest
stuffs.description: I hid my things in a chest inside the factory

stuffs.name: Chest in the stairwell
stuffs.description: In the chest under the stairs there's a secret stash.

stuffs.name: Factory chest
stuffs.description: I hid it in the chest, nobody will check anyway.

stuffs.name: The bag is on the support beam
stuffs.description: Dropped the bag out the window. Will pick it up later.

stuffs.name: Trash bin
stuffs.description: Kolyan and I had a nice walk at the Agroprom. We found a bunch of junk, but managed to hide a few things. We put the chest in the trash bin.

stuffs.name: Safe under the tree
stuffs.description: I found a safe under a fallen tree. Going to hide everything there for now.

stuffs.name: Things in the pipe
stuffs.description: I threw the things into the pipe, will get them later. I had to, otherwise I would have obviously taken them along. Just hope they don't get wet.

stuffs.name: Radioactive pipe
stuffs.description: The goods are in the old pipe, we'll have to tell the guys that. I'm not climbing in there.

stuffs.name: The pile
stuffs.description: Ran away from the base, to hell with them! Dodged the stalkers' fire. Hid my stuff in a pile in a pipe.  I'll hang out here until they leave, then I'll pick it up.

stuffs.name: Safe under the bush
stuffs.description: There is a half buried safe under the bush - that's where I hide everything.

stuffs.name: Archive box
stuffs.description: They discovered the chest under the support beam. Someone was dragging it along all the way from Scientific Research Institute. Let's wait for the windflier and then pick it up.

stuffs.name: Under the trap door
stuffs.description: Hid my stuff in an iron capsule

stuffs.name: Under the bush by the wall
stuffs.description: There is a half buried safe under the bush - that's where I hide everything.

stuffs.name: Chest from the institute
stuffs.description: Good chest for collecting extra junk

stuffs.name: Agrosafe
stuffs.description: Hid it in the safe, but then the soldiers came and now I can't get the goods.

stuffs.name: The body of the truck
stuffs.description: Threw my junk in the pipe - will get it later.

stuffs.name: Rotted log
stuffs.description: Take the things from the rotted log

stuffs.name: Zavhoz chest
stuffs.description: Good chest for collecting extra junk. The institute's equipment inventory was once there.

stuffs.name: Metalworking inventory
stuffs.description: Good chest for small things. I kept my metalworking instruments in a chest like that at home.

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the cross
stuffs.description: Hid the bit of goodies under the cross by the mountain

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the log
stuffs.description: Stuck the goods into the log. Don't think they'll find it.

stuffs.name: Backpack under the bridge
stuffs.description: Stuck the backpack under the bridge. Let it stay there for now.

stuffs.name: Car with the secret stash
stuffs.description: Put the chest into the car by the swamp

stuffs.name: Secret stash in a stump
stuffs.description: There's a secret stash in a stump - good place for it

stuffs.name: Chest with supplies
stuffs.description: Found a great chest on the farm. I'll keep the supplies there for now.

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the pipe
stuffs.description: Threw my things into the pipe. Will pick them up later.

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the pine tree
stuffs.description: Hid the backpack under a pine tree

stuffs.name: Government chest
stuffs.description: The newbie ended up stealing the chest from the bandits. He put it into the Niva which turned up side down. He says that by the looks of it, it's a government chest. We'll have to arm our guys and take it.

stuffs.name: Chest
stuffs.description: There are robberies everywhere. They're even stealing even from their own... but they'll never find my chest

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the manhole
stuffs.description: Hid my things in the manhole. Maybe they'll come in handy some day.

stuffs.name: Stalker's backpack
stuffs.description: Threw the backpack under a tree. Otherwise, I wouldn't have escaped the bandits.

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Put my junk into a pipe, will pick it up later

stuffs.name: Hidden safe
stuffs.description: Everything I stole from Borov I hid away in a safe under the pine tree. Now I have to wait it out while they finish freaking out.

stuffs.name: Warehouse in the train car
stuffs.description: The temporary headquarters are in the train car, as is the chest with the supplies

stuffs.name: Secret place in the pipe
stuffs.description: Barely made it into the pipe under the road. Now I'll have a place to hide me backpack

stuffs.name: Chest with goods
stuffs.description: Threw the goods into the chest - will get them later

stuffs.name: Secret stash behind the pipe
stuffs.description: I'm hiding the goodies behind the pipe - it's hard to get to, but at least they won't take off with it

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the electricity room
stuffs.description: Found some cartriges in the electricity room

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the chest
stuffs.description: We left everything that we found in the chest, we'll pick it up when we're returning

stuffs.name: Hidden backpack
stuffs.description: Hid the backpack of the newbie, and he never found it

stuffs.name: Forgotten chest
stuffs.description: The chest was left in the van - needs to be picked up

stuffs.name: Safe at the gas station
stuffs.description: Found a safe at the gas station and hid my goods in it. Seems like nobody ever goes there.

stuffs.name: Chest
stuffs.description: Dragged the chest on the cistern

stuffs.name: Safe at the gas station
stuffs.description: Hid the supplies in the safe at the gas station.

stuffs.name: Chest in the car
stuffs.description: There's some chest in the car at the bandits' camp. We need to sneak into the car and check it out - I feel there's something in there

stuffs.name: Chest in the secret stash
stuffs.description: Put the chest into the secret stash - it's a reliable place

stuffs.name: The left-behind backpack
stuffs.description: Left the backpack in an abandoned building. Good, nobody's around.

stuffs.name: Borov's secret stash
stuffs.description: We'll store the goods in a safe in a nondescript place. If the soldiers don't come today, then they'll come tomorrow. They won't look around for very long so the most valuable stuff will be left for me.

stuffs.name: Backpack in a secret place
stuffs.description: Stashed away the backpack by the building

stuffs.name: Nondescript chest
stuffs.description: Stuck the goodies in a nondescript chest. Will get them later

stuffs.name: Hidden backpack
stuffs.description: Hid the backpack under the car, nobody will bother looking there

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the car
stuffs.description: Hid the goodies in the car right under the bandits' noses, didn't have any time to look for a better place

stuffs.name: The backpack that was left behind
stuffs.description: A large pack of dogs went after me. If I didn't leave my backpack I wouldn't have made it to the gate

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the cross
stuffs.description: Everything that was left they buried under the cross

stuffs.name: Backpack
stuffs.description: Dropped my backpack here - it'll be easier that way

stuffs.name: Supplies in the bunker
stuffs.description: Ammo of the Duty's security checkpoint is stored in a bunker, but nobody's keeping an eye on the chest

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: I saw how a dutyer stuck something in the pipe by the gate

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the cross
stuffs.description: All of this belonged to him, might as well stay here for the time being

stuffs.name: Backpack
stuffs.description: I'm going to the bar, left the backpack in the hangar

stuffs.name: Swithboard with a secret stash
stuffs.description: They say that there's something valuable hidden on the Duty's territory in the switchboard.

stuffs.name: Secret stash on the tower
stuffs.description: I stuck the chest in top of the tower in front of the Duty - no one will notice it

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Hid it in the pipe under the stairs

stuffs.name: Arny's secret stash
stuffs.description: Hid the goods not far from the bar, behind the anomalies - nobody will get in there. And even if they got there they wouldn't know how to open it. But it's all very simple - just pull up slightly at the door, and everything will open.

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Buried the goods not far from the bar

stuffs.name: Chest
stuffs.description: By the bar, in a chest

stuffs.name: Small chest
stuffs.description: Hid the chest on a side-street by the bar

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Buried it under the cross behind the pine trees

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Under the cross, not far from the passage into the Dark Territory

stuffs.name: Small chest
stuffs.description: Hid the chest with the antirad in a pipe by the Arena

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Hid my crap in a pipe under the tower

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: There's a secret stash under the cross

stuffs.name: Hidden backpack
stuffs.description: Hid the backpack behind the iron plate

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the cross
stuffs.description: Stashed the goodies under the cross

stuffs.name: Chest under the small house
stuffs.description: Hid a little something in the chest under the little house. Shouldn't forget about it.

stuffs.name: Stalker's backpack
stuffs.description: I was about to stick the backpack under the steps, when those jerks appeared. Man, how will I get it back?

stuffs.name: Secret stash behind the tree
stuffs.description: There's a half buried safe in the corner behind the tree. That's where all my junk will be for now.

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the garage
stuffs.description: They hid everything in a chest in the garage that they took over during the rain.

stuffs.name: Hidden chest
stuffs.description: Hid some things in the chest behind the booth

stuffs.name: Backpack in the secret stash
stuffs.description: Stuck the backpack in a hole. Seems unnoticeable from above.

stuffs.name: Chest in a safe spot
stuffs.description: Hid the small chest in a safe spot

stuffs.name: Secret stash of the stalker
stuffs.description: My backpack is up right under the roof. It's there for a rainy day.

stuffs.name: Safe in the house
stuffs.description: They say there's a safe in that little house, and that there's something in it

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the pipe
stuffs.description: Hid it in the house in a pipe. Careful, everything's out of whack there

stuffs.name: Hidden chest
stuffs.description: Take what we talked about from the chest. Usually nobody looks in there

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the cross
stuffs.description: Hid it under the cross on a side street

stuffs.name: Secret stash under the concrete
stuffs.description: They hid the extra supplies under the concrete at the construction site

stuffs.name: Secret stash of the Lucky One
stuffs.description: In case we need to take off quickly, we'll put the habar into the chest at the construction site.

stuffs.name: Nychka
stuffs.description: Hid it in one of the side streets at the construction site

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the pipe
stuffs.description: Stuck everything into some pipe - will pick it up later

stuffs.description: Hid the medicine in a chest not far from the construction site

stuffs.name: Chest in the crane
stuffs.description: Dragged the chest into the cabin of the crane

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the manhole
stuffs.description: Hid my goods in a manhole in the corner.

stuffs.name: The dropped backpack
stuffs.description: Went after the artifact and got into an anomaly. I was barely able to walk and dropped the backpack in the corner.

stuffs.name: Small chest under the roof
stuffs.description: Stuck the chest right under the roof by the tower so that nobody would notice.

stuffs.name: Secret stash in the pipe
stuffs.description: We hid what we found in the pipe not far from the construction site.

stuffs.name: Secret stash
stuffs.description: Stuck all the goods into the log. Don't think they'll find it.

stuffs.description: Dropped the backpack off by the crane

stuffs.name: The loot is in the car
stuffs.description: The goodies are hidden in the car not far from the territory. The radiation is not very high.

stuffs.name: Old backpack
stuffs.description: They say there's somebody's goodies there, but they can't get to it because of the radiation.

stuffs.name: Secret stash of a grouping
stuffs.description: They say that here there's a secret stash of some grouping. I only wonder how they got here with the radiation?

stuffs.name: Backpack of the tester
stuffs.description: Another volunteer stalker croaked because another prototype didn't protect him from the radiation. He only made it to the middle of the territory, and stayed there. Saharov wants to take more precise measurements, but I won't go, else I'll end up staying there myself, not far from the territory.

stuffs.name: Old secret stash
stuffs.description: They say that there is somebody's habar, but there's no way to get there because of the radiation.

stuffs.name: Secret stash of the scientist
stuffs.description: Gotta take off. Saharov and Kruglov are total psychos - they want me to go with some stalker into the center of radiation. Screw them, as soon as I gather all the supplies in the manhole, I'm taking off.

stuffs.name: Goodies in the safe
stuffs.description: They say that there's a half-buried safe in the forest and there's a bunch of goodies inside

stuffs.name: Package for Duty
stuffs.description: They told them not to fly over the Scorcher, and look what happend. They landed in the middle of the forest, and it's unlikely that anyone survived. We were supposed to get the stuff that was with them.

stuffs.name: Supplies of the reckless group
stuffs.description: They say that the supplies of the faction, who were trying to get to the center of the Zone, are still under the radiation of the Scorcher. None of them returned, and the supplies remained there waiting for someone to pick them up.

stuffs.name: Goodies of the leader of former faction
stuffs.description: They say that the leader of some former faction croaked here, and there was a valuable amount of goodies with him

stuffs.name: Fang's goodies
stuffs.description: They buried Fang in Pripyat under a monument. They left all of his goodies with him - it's not right to take away from the dead.

stuffs.name: Supplies of the leader of Freedom
stuffs.description: The last that they knew about him is that he was the sole survivor after the scorcher. He left all the supplies in some old supermarket, and moved on out. Everything went not the way it was planned, and that was the best leader of Freedom in all of our history.
